Uber Just ask an Uber driver to describe his or her worst passenger and you'll hear tales of vomiting passengers to screaming matches to hookups in the backseat.

One driver has even told me (complete with pictures) of ending up with a bullet in his car after unknowingly taking a passenger to an area with a reputation for drug deals.
